code: @Override public String getGroupId(String artifactId) {     Dependency dependency = find(artifactId).     return (dependency != null) ? dependency.getGroupId() : null. }
@Override public String getArtifactId(String id) {     Dependency dependency = find(id).     return (dependency != null) ? dependency.getArtifactId() : null. }

private Dependency find(String id) {     if (StringUtils.countOccurrencesOf(id, ":") == 2) {         String[] tokens = id.split(":").         return new Dependency(tokens[0], tokens[1], tokens[2]).     }     if (id != null) {         if (id.startsWith("spring-boot")) {             return new Dependency("org.springframework.boot", id, this.dependencyManagement.getSpringBootVersion()).         }         return this.dependencyManagement.find(id).     }     return null. }
@Override public String getVersion(String module) {     Dependency dependency = find(module).     return (dependency != null) ? dependency.getVersion() : null. }
